2002年2月下旬宣传首部《生化危机》电影期间，[[米拉·乔沃维奇|米拉·乔沃维奇]]和导演[[保罗·W·S·安德森|保罗·W·S·安德森]]就曾探讨续集计划。安德森自称完成第一部的剧本后就开始写第二部，计划在续集中让艾莉丝和吉尔·瓦伦汀一起出现。乔沃维奇表示，只要第一部电影取得成功，她愿意回归续作。<ref name="MSN">{{cite web | date = 2002-02-27 | title = MSN Talks to Director Paul Anderson and Actress Milla Jovovich | accessdate = 2009-10-05 | url = http://www.countingdown.com/movies/13839/news?item_id=554777 | work = [[MSN|MSN]] Live | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091005063213/http://www.countingdown.com/movies/13839/news?item_id=554777 | archivedate = 2009-10-05}}</ref>同年三月上旬，在第一部电影中扮演马特·安德森的[[艾力·馬比烏斯|艾力·馬比烏斯]]声称续集已经确定并以淙熊市为背景，片中还会出现复仇邪神<ref name="syfy">{{cite web | url = http://www.scifi.com/scifiwire/art-film.html?2002-03/04/13.00.film | title = Mabius Talks Resident Evil 2 | date = 2002-03-04 | work = [[Syfy|Syfy]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090414193046/http://www.scifi.com/scifiwire/art-film.html?2002-03%2F04%2F13.00.film | archivedate = 2009-04-14 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2020-08-21 }}</ref>。2002年中期，[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影視娛樂]][[綠燈_(電影製作)|正式批准]]项目，安德森因决定执掌《[[异形大战铁血战士|异形大战铁血战士]]》不担任续集导演，但继续出任[[編劇|編劇]]和[[电影制片人|制片人]]<ref name="comtwo">{{cite video | people = Paul W.S. Anderson, Jeremy Bolt | title = ''Resident Evil: Apocalypse Writer and Producer Commentary'' | medium = DVD | publisher = Sony Entertainment | date = 2004}}</ref>。安德森用游戏《[[生化危機3_最終逃脫|生化危機3 最終逃脫]]》作为剧情基础，并加入他很喜欢的一些电影元素，如《[[纽约大逃亡|纽约大逃亡]]》中的大围墙，以及《[[最后一个人|最后一个人]]》中的荒废城市<ref name="comtwo" />。亚历山大·维特（{{lang|en|Alexander Witt}}）获聘执导本片，此时剧本已经完成，但首次导演长片电影的维特还是向安德森和制片人杰里米·博尔特（{{lang|en|Jeremy Bolt}}）提出建议，剧本因此略有调整<ref name="otto">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170810092623/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/08/23/interview-alexander-witt | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2004/08/23/interview-alexander-witt | title = Interview: Alexander Witt | last = Otto | first = Jeff | date = 2004-08-23 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | archivedate = 2017-08-10 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

=== 演员敲定 ===
出演前一部电影的演员仅有乔沃维奇参演续集，起初有报导称馬比烏斯会回归饰演变成复仇邪神的安德森<ref name="syfy" /><ref name="talent" />，但最终实际出演的是马修·泰勒，馬比烏斯仅在闪回镜头中的上一部电影素材片段出现<ref>{{cite video | title = ''Resident Evil: Apocalypse'' | medium = DVD | publisher = Sony Entertainment | date = 2004}}</ref>。第一部电影不包含游戏角色，但续集从一开始就打算增加<ref name="over">{{cite video | people = Robert Kulzer, Dan Carmody, Jeremy Bolt | title = Game Over | medium = Resident Evil: Apocalypse, DVD featurette | publisher = Sony Entertainment | date = 2004}}</ref>。[[吉娜·菲利普斯|吉娜·菲利普斯]]（{{lang|en|Gina Philips}}）原定出演[[克蕾兒·雷德菲爾|克蕾兒·雷德菲爾]]，她拒绝后剧组又找上[[艾米莉·贝吉尔|艾米莉·贝吉尔]]（{{lang|en|Emily Bergl}}），贝吉尔也在开拍前退出，结果角色取消<ref>{{cite web | url = https://screenrant.com/resident-evil-movies-best-worst-scenes-final-chapter/ | title = Everything The Resident Evil Movies Got Right (And Wrong) | last = Chapman | first = Tom | date = 2017-02-19 | work = [[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191206113649/https://screenrant.com/resident-evil-movies-best-worst-scenes-final-chapter/ | archivedate = 2019-12-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，直到本片2007年的续集《[[惡靈古堡3：大滅絕|生化危机3：灭绝]]》中才出现，由[[艾丽·拉特|艾丽·拉特]]出演。安德森起初打算找[[娜塔莎·韓絲翠|娜塔莎·韓絲翠]]出演瓦伦汀，但她当时没空<ref name="talent">{{cite web | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2002/05/21/anderson-shopping-for-resident-talent | title = Anderson Shopping for Resident Talent | date = 2002-05-21 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170804120920/http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/05/21/anderson-shopping-for-resident-talent | archivedate = 2020-08-21}}</ref>，接着[[米拉·索维诺|米拉·索维诺]]又谢绝出演<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2003/04/17/resident-evil-nemesis-character-expose | title = Resident Evil: Nemesis Character Exposé | last = Davidson | first = Paul | date = 2003-04-17 | work = IGN | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170918065123/http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/04/17/resident-evil-nemesis-character-expose | archivedate = 2017-09-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，最终接演的[[西耶娜·盖尔利|西耶娜·盖尔利]]通过《生化危机》游戏研究人物动作和姿势，为演出准备<ref name="cast" /><ref name="babes">{{cite video | people = Milla Jovovich, Sienna Guillory | title = Game Babes | medium = Resident Evil: Apocalypse, DVD featurette | publisher = Sony Entertainment | date = 2004}}</ref>。{{lang|en|L.J.}}一角本是特意为[[史努比狗狗|史努比狗狗]]创作，但他中途退出后艾普斯接演，为此剧本经过修改，确保角色与演员特质相符<ref name="comtwo" />。此外，[[伊凡塞斯|伊凡塞斯]]吉他手[[本·穆迪|本·穆迪]]（{{lang|en|Ben Moody}}）在片中客串出镜，扮演齐诺比耶夫杀死的丧尸<ref name="cast">{{cite video | people = Milla Jovovich, Oded Fehr, Sienna Guillory | title = ''Resident Evil: Apocalypse Cast Commentary'' | medium = DVD | publisher = Sony Entertainment | date = 2004}}</ref>。

=== 拍摄 ===
[[File:Sienna_and_Jill.png|thumb]]在片中的服装是根据1999年游戏《[[生化危機3_最終逃脫|生化危機3 最終逃脫]]》中瓦伦汀的服饰设计]]

《生化危机2：启示录》在加拿大[[安大略省|安大略省]][[多伦多|多伦多]]拍摄，周围郊区用于为淙熊市取景<ref name="kehr">{{cite web | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2004/09/10/movies/call-to-arms-with-trouble-right-here-in-zombie-city.html | title = Call to Arms, With Trouble Right Here in Zombie City | last = Kehr | first = Dave | date = 2004-09-10 | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191228132532/https://www.nytimes.com/2004/09/10/movies/call-to-arms-with-trouble-right-here-in-zombie-city.html | archivedate = 2019-12-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。摄影由克里斯蒂安·泽巴尔特（{{lang|en|Christian Sebaldt}}）和德里克·罗杰斯（{{lang|en|Derek Rogers}}）负责<ref name="bfi" />，取景地共有47处<ref name="over" />，需要搭建的外景地很少<ref name="comtwo" />。为便于拍摄，城里多个街区一度关闭，爱德华王子高架桥（{{lang|en|Prince Edward Viaduct}}）甚至封闭三天之久，部分镜头还需在[[多倫多市政廳|多倫多市政廳]]外拍摄两星期<ref name="building">{{cite video | people = Jeremy Bolt, Dan Carmody | title = Building Raccoon City | medium = Resident Evil: Apocalypse, DVD featurette | publisher = Sony Entertainment | date = 2004}}</ref>。乔沃维奇和马修·泰勒前后六周每天花好几个小时一起为艾莉丝和复仇邪神的战斗场面练习武术<ref name="running">{{cite video | people = Matthew Taylor, Steve Lucescu | title = "running", Jumping, Fighting | medium = Resident Evil: Apocalypse, DVD featurette | publisher = Sony Entertainment | date = 2004}}</ref>。根据剧本安排，两个角色本应在火车站大战，镜头主要关注人物和道具，但导演最终决定缩短打斗场面时长，改在多伦多市政厅外的开阔地摄制<ref name="comtwo" />。扮演丧尸的演员在“新丧尸训练营”接受[[编舞|编舞]]为期四天的训练，确保他们行为和动作一致<ref>{{cite video | people = Derek Aasland, Sharon Moore | title = Zombie Choreography | medium = Resident Evil: Apocalypse, DVD featurette | publisher = Sony Entertainment | date = 2004}}</ref>。安德森及其他剧组人员一度打算提升丧尸的行动速度，但感觉这样与游戏的根本要素冲突而放弃<ref name="comtwo" />。因忙于其他项目，安德森只有几天来到片场，但他还是在拍摄期间通过电子邮件与维特交流，讨论对白和制作变更事宜<ref name="otto" />。剧本原定让艾莉丝通过[[念力|念力]]逃出安布雷拉后与瓦伦汀汇合，结局修改时，电影约半数镜头已经拍完<ref name="comtwo" />。

第一部《生化危机》电影只采用游戏的大致框架，续集则纳入许多具体内容，如场景重现<ref name="over" />。《生化危机2：启示录》从《[[生化危機_聖女密碼|生化危機 聖女密碼]]》中包含克蕾兒·雷德菲爾的[[剧情画面|过场动画介绍]]汲取灵感，插入艾莉丝顶着安布雷拉直升机火力跑过大楼的情节<ref name="building" />。《生化危機3 最終逃脫》的片头是本片中淙熊市被丧尸占领，警察和安布雷拉军人反击桥段的灵感来源<ref name="comtwo" />。瓦伦汀在片中的服饰根据《生化危機3 最終逃脫》设计，包括[[无肩带背心|无肩带背心]]和[[迷你裙|迷你裙]]<ref name="harper">{{cite journal | url = https://www.ejumpcut.org/archive/jc49.2007/HarperResEvil/text.html | title = "I could kiss you, you bitch": race, gender, and sexuality in Resident Evil and Resident Evil 2: Apocalypse | last = Harper | first = Stephen | date = 2007 | journal = Jump Cut: A Review of Contemporary Media | issue = 49 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200818162638/http://www.ejumpcut.org/archive/jc49.2007/HarperResEvil/text.html | archivedate = 2020-08-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。安德森曾考虑多种方式让瓦伦汀的服装显得合理，如声称这是她的[[臥底|臥底]]装扮等，但最终决定不予理会，因为会质疑服装与人物身份不符的人“或许也不该来看《生化危机》电影”<ref name="comtwo" />。电影还包括第一部《[[生化危机_(1996年游戏)|生化危机]]》和《[[生化危機2|生化危機2]]》的多种元素，如地址地点名称、角色动作、道具和镜头角度<ref name="comtwo" />。

=== 特效 ===
本片采用的特效手段包括[[色键|色键]]、[[计算机成像|计算机成像]]、[[接景|接景]]、[[推轨镜头|推轨镜头]]、钢丝擦除和[[比例模型|比例模型]]<ref name="smoke">{{cite video | people = Alison O'Brien, Kyle Menzes, Eric Robertson | title = Smoke and Mirrors | medium = Resident Evil: Apocalypse, DVD featurette | publisher = Sony Entertainment | date = 2004}}</ref>。复仇邪神是用特殊服装构建，仅用计算机成像技术调整眼部<ref name="smoke"/>。泰勒获选出演复仇邪神的主要原因是体形，他身高2.04米，体重145公斤，服装特别根据他的体形制作，重29公斤<ref name="running" />。虽然人物形态已经非常庞大，但部分镜头还是通过调整[[長寬比_(影像)|长宽比]]将复仇邪神扩大一到两成<ref name="comtwo" />。片中的变异丧尸“舔食者”完全是计算机成像，特效组本在部分镜头采用[[电子动画|电子动画]]，但效果不够理想<ref name="smoke"/>。舔食者的特效制作是由多家特效公司递交初步设计竞标，最终{{lang|en|[[C.O.R.E.|C.O.R.E.]]}}数字图像公司胜出，该公司为电影制作超过250个特效镜头，其中包括用乔沃维奇的脸取代特技替身，但最具挑战的还是舔食者<ref name="fx" />。艾莉丝的大部分特技镜头都是乔沃维奇亲自上场，但保险公司不允许她参与更加危险镜头的拍摄<ref name="cast" />。[[狂暴电影|狂暴电影]]（{{lang|en|Frantic Films}}）为本片制作78个特效镜头，包括[[曳光彈|曳光彈]]开火、[[枪口火焰|枪口火焰]]、激光和慢动作，使用的特效软件包括{{lang|en|[[Blackmagic_Fusion|Blackmagic Fusion]]}}、{{lang|en|[[3ds_Max|Autodesk 3ds Max]]}}和内部软件<ref name="fx">{{cite journal | last = Dillon | first = Mark | date = 2004-10-25 | title = Shops join forces to wreak apocalypse | journal = Playback: Canada's Broadcast and Production Journal | page = 17}}</ref>。神秘人公司（{{lang|en|Mr. X Inc.}}）也为电影制作部分特效，如多伦多市政厅倒塌的镜头。为此公司花费四个月按一比六搭建13米高的比例模型，上有1600块玻璃，每块都接有爆炸装置。<ref name="smoke" />[[數碼中間片|數碼中間片]]由{{lang|en|[[Framestore|Framestore]]}}完成。片中色彩在后期制作期间大幅改动，令整体色调变暗，同时强化血液和血块亮度。复仇邪神服装的颜色也经调整，让角色看起来更活灵活现。此外，艾莉丝和瓦伦汀的镜头也有修整，让皮肤更有光泽，嘴唇更红。<ref name="comtwo" />

=== 电影原声带 ===
《生化危机2：启示录》的电影原声带于2004年8月31日发行，其中既有片中的[[另类金属|另类金属]]歌曲，也有以电影为“灵感”创作的曲目。{{lang|en|[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]}}的约翰尼·洛夫图斯（{{lang|en|Johnny Loftus}}）对原声带评分三星（最高五星），批为“无良摇钱树”，有意迎合电影的青少年男目标观众，在他看来，原声带内容“咄咄逼人而狂躁，整体呈现世界末日般的基调，与根据电子游戏改编、剧情大致是炸飞疯狂丧尸的电影很搭”。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.allmusic.com/album/resident-evil-apocalypse-original-soundtrack-mw0000158803 | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse [Original Soundtrack] | last = Loftus | first = Johnny | work = [[AllMusic|AllMusic]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190505220920/https://www.allmusic.com/album/resident-evil-apocalypse-original-soundtrack-mw0000158803 | archivedate = 2019-05-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

[[电影配乐|电影配乐]]由杰夫·丹纳（{{lang|en|Jeff Danna}}）作曲，[[愛樂管弦樂團|伦敦爱乐管弦乐团]]演奏，2004年9月28日发行<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2016-08-17 | deadurl = no | work = [[AllMusic|AllMusic]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160817223324/http://www.allmusic.com/album/resident-evil-apocalypse-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-mw0000139707 | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse [Original Motion Picture Soundtrack] | url = https://www.allmusic.com/album/resident-evil-apocalypse-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-mw0000139707}}</ref>。{{lang|en|Soundtrack.net}}网站的迈克·布伦南（{{lang|en|Mike Brennan}}）评分两星半（最高五星），称赞乐曲融合管弦乐和电子音乐风格，但觉得作品在主题发展、音调变化上还大有进步余地<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.soundtrack.net/album/resident-evil-apocalypse/ | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse | last = Brennan | first = Mike | date = 2005-04-10 | work = Soundtrack.net | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305011404/http://www.soundtrack.net/album/resident-evil-apocalypse/ | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 发行 ==

=== 营销和票房 ===
[[馬可斯·尼斯佩|馬可斯·尼斯佩]]获聘为电影制作[[预告片|预告片]]《再生》（{{lang|en|''Regenerate''}}）。预告片起初像是安布雷拉的嫩肤产品广告，但画面中的女子突然变成丧尸。截至2004年5月，电影官方网站提供的预告片已有850万次下载。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2004/film/markets-festivals/nispel-takes-an-evil-turn-1117904191/ | title = Nispel takes an ‘Evil’ turn | last = LaPorte | first = Nicole | date = 2004-05-02 | work = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20171204112639/http://variety.com/2004/film/markets-festivals/nispel-takes-an-evil-turn-1117904191/ | archivedate = 2017-12-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>电影在背景画面的电视机上显示部分预告片内容，[[片尾彩蛋|片尾彩蛋]]也有一部分<ref name="comtwo" />。2004年7月，电影的剧场正式预告片在[[雅虎电影|雅虎电影]]（{{lang|en|Yahoo! Movies}}）发布<ref>{{cite web | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse | work = Yahoo! Movies | archivedate = 2008-05-18 | url = https://movies.yahoo.com/movies/feature/residentevilapocalypse.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080518033215/https://movies.yahoo.com/movies/feature/residentevilapocalypse.html}}</ref>。[[基思·迪坎迪多|基思·迪坎迪多]]（{{lang|en|Keith DeCandido}}）将电影改写成小说，2004年8月底由[[西蒙與舒斯特|西蒙與舒斯特]]出版<ref>{{cite book | last = DeCandido | first = Keith R. A. | date = 2004-08-31 | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse | publisher = [[西蒙與舒斯特|Simon & Schuster]] | isbn = 978-0743499378}}</ref>。

2004年9月10日，《生化危机2：启示录》在美国首映并登顶票房榜，第一个周末进账超过2300万美元<ref name = "gross" />。影片在香港、新加坡、马来西亚、菲律宾和墨西哥均一经上映就占据票房榜首位，在日本、法国和巴西的表现都很好，但在英国被恐怖片《[[恐懼鬥室|电锯惊魂]]》抢去风头，在瑞典的表现也不佳<ref>{{cite journal | url = https://variety.com/2004/film/box-office/shark-tale-plays-swimmingly-overseas-1117912052/ | accessdate = 2020-08-21 | title = Film/International: 'shark tale' plays swimmingly overseas | last = Groves | first = Dan | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | volume = 396 | issue = 9 | pages = 12 | date = 2004-10-18 | archive-date = 2020-08-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200821142049/https://variety.com/2004/film/box-office/shark-tale-plays-swimmingly-overseas-1117912052/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = 'Collateral' leads newcomers in tepid o'seas sesh | last = Groves | first = Dan | journal = Variety | volume = 396 | issue = 8 | url = https://variety.com/2004/film/box-office/collateral-leads-in-tepid-o-seas-sesh-1117911687/ | pages = 10 | date = 2004-10-11 | accessdate = 2020-08-21 | archive-date = 2020-08-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200821142212/https://variety.com/2004/film/box-office/collateral-leads-in-tepid-o-seas-sesh-1117911687/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，票房仅47万3550美元<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/releasegroup/gr1399935493/ | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse - Foreign | work = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20180103234737/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=residentevilapocalypse.htm | archivedate = 2018-01-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《生化危机2：启示录》在加拿大收入超六百万[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]，是2004年票房最高的加拿大本土制作电影<ref>{{cite journal | last = Dillon | first = Mark | date = 2005-03-28 | title = Genie 2005: Prix Jutra, part deux | journal = Playback: Canada's Broadcast and Production Journal | page = 1}}</ref>。本片最终以4500万成本在全球营收一亿2934万4835美元<ref name="gross" />，超越收入一亿零298万4862美元的前作<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2372765185/ | title = Resident Evil | work = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191221204738/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2372765185/ | archivedate = 2019-12-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
根据[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]网站收集的132篇评论文章，《生化危机2：启示录》评论认可度仅两成，在全系列六部电影中垫底<ref name="Rotten Tomatoes" /><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/franchise/resident_evil | title = Resident Evil | work = [[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | archive-date = 2020-06-08 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200608222854/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/franchise/resident_evil}}</ref>。网站上的评论共识写道：“《生化危机2：启示录》动作很多，但情节和创意不值一提”<ref name="Rotten Tomatoes">{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/resident_evil_apocalypse | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200819122018/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/resident_evil_apocalypse | work = Rotten Tomatoes | deadurl = no | archive-date = 2020-08-19}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}根据26篇评论打出的评分为35（满分100）<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.metacritic.com/movie/resident-evil-apocalypse | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse 2004 | work = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727183527/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/resident-evil-apocalypse | archive-date = 2020-07-27}}</ref>。[[影院评分|影院评分]]开展的观众调查打分为“{{lang|en|B}}”（最高为{{lang|en|A}}，最低{{lang|en|F}}）<ref>需在“{{lang|en|FIND CINEMASCORE}}”下面的搜索框内输出电影原名，页面会自动显示评分：{{cite web | url = http://www.cinemascore.com/ | title = CinemaScore | work = [[影院评分|CinemaScore]] | accessdate = 2020-08-21 | archive-date = 2019-05-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190518162710/https://www.cinemascore.com/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[伦纳德·马尔丁|伦纳德·马尔丁]]（{{lang|en|Leonard Maltin}}）在著作《[[伦纳德·马尔丁电影指南|伦纳德·马尔丁电影指南]]》（''{{lang|en|Leonard Maltin's Movie Guide}}''）中对本片的评分为“炸弹”，认为影片令人筋疲力尽，名为续集倒更像[[重製|重拍]]<ref>{{cite book | last = Maltin | first = Leonard | date = 2005 | title = Leonard Maltin's Movie Guide 2006 | publisher = Signet | page = 1072 | isbn = 978-0451216090 | url = https://archive.org/details/leonardmaltins00malt/page/1072 | accessdate = 2020-08-21}}</ref>。[[罗杰·伊伯特|罗杰·伊伯特]]的评分仅为半星（最高四星），认为本片没有任何意义，纯属浪费时间；在他看来，电影缺乏智慧和想象力，暴力和特技也没有娱乐效果<ref>{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200625035826/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/resident-evil-apocalypse-2004 | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/resident-evil-apocalypse-2004 | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse | last = Ebert | first = Roger | author-link = 罗杰·伊伯特 | date = 2005-09-10 | work = [[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun-Times]] | archive-date = 2020-06-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。凯莉·里基（{{lang|en|Carrie Rickey}}）在《[[費城詢問報|費城詢問報]]》发文给予本片一星（最高四星），认为即便是对那些喜欢生物恐怖片的观众而言，《生化危机2：启示录》也“实在普通”<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.inquirer.com/philly/entertainment/movies/MovieReviewID_20040910_inq_weekend_CRKEVIL.html | title = Fighting evil in the near nude: Yet another video-game flick | last = Rickey | first = Carrie | date = 2004-09-10 | newspaper = [[費城詢問報|The Philadelphia Inquirer]] | archive-url = https://archive.is/20171205002310/http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/movies/MovieReviewID_20040910_inq_weekend_CRKEVIL.html | archive-date = 2017-12-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》刊登[[戴夫·基尔|戴夫·基尔]]（{{lang|en|Dave Kehr}}）的评论，称赞安德森的剧本，认为电影节奏明快、内容风趣而高明，能够卓有成效地让观众感到肚里翻江倒海<ref name="kehr" />。《[[俄勒冈人报|俄勒冈人报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Oregonian''}}）的{{lang|en|M·E}}·罗素（{{lang|en|M. E. Russell}}）称：“坏消息是电影蠢到遗臭万年，好消息是这种蠢还有点好笑”<ref>{{cite news | last = Russell | first = M. E. | date = 2004-09-10 | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse | newspaper = The Oregonian}}</ref>。内森·拉宾在《[[影音俱乐部|影音俱乐部]]》发文指出，《生化危机2：启示录》情节发展实在太慢，达不到优秀电影的基本要求，“但到乔沃维奇终于开始痛扁丧尸后，问题解决了”<ref>{{cite web | date = 2004-09-14 | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse | url = https://film.avclub.com/resident-evil-apocalypse-1798199945 | author = Nathan Rabin | work = [[影音俱樂部|The A.V. Club]] | publisher = [[洋葱报|The Onion]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191124091408/https://film.avclub.com/resident-evil-apocalypse-1798199945 | archivedate = 2019-11-24}}</ref>。《[[乡村之声报|乡村之声报]]》（''{{lang|en|The Village Voice}}''）刊登本·肯尼斯堡（{{lang|en|Ben Kenigsberg}}）的评论，认为本片部分内容还算吓人，但动作场面和纯粹拖时间的内容实在太多，而且讽刺程度尚有欠缺<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.villagevoice.com/2004/09/07/film-203/ | title = Film | last = Kenigsberg | first = Ben | date = 2004-09-07 | newspaper = The Village Voice | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180915155720/https://www.villagevoice.com/2004/09/07/film-203/ | archive-date = 2018-09-15 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的格雷戈里·基施林（{{lang|en|Gregory Kirschling}}）对电影评分“{{lang|en|D}}−”（最高{{lang|en|A}}+），他称赞乔沃维奇的演出，但感觉其他演员“拍的电影[[非戲院首映|都只能发DVD]]”<ref>{{cite web | url = https://ew.com/article/2004/09/24/resident-evil-apocalypse-2/ | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse | last = Kirschling | first = Gregory | date = 2004-09-24 | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190523142321/https://ew.com/article/2004/09/24/resident-evil-apocalypse-2/ | archivedate = 2019-05-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。不过，《{{lang|en|[[Cinefantastique|Cinefantastique]]}}》（字面义为“神奇影院”）的评论反而认为乔沃维奇的演出看起来很无聊，盖尔利对吉尔·瓦伦汀的诠释堪称本片救星<ref>{{cite journal | last = Clarke | first = Frederick S. | year = 2005 | title = Resident Evil: Apocalypse | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=Hy4nAQAAIAAJ&q=jill+valentine&redir_esc=y | journal = Cinefantastique | volume = 37 | page = 63 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2017-12-21 | accessdate = 2020-08-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171221142354/https://books.google.com/books?id=Hy4nAQAAIAAJ&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=jill+valentine}}</ref>。

=== 影响 ===
2009年，《[[时代杂志|时代杂志]]》评选史上十大[[电影版|电子游戏改编]]烂片，《生化危机2：启示录》榜上有名，文章批评当时已经上映的三部《生化危机》系列电影，但只有第二部上榜主要是因为原作本来就很垃圾，为垃圾电影拍续集只会导致更多续集面世<ref>{{cite news | title = Top 10 Worst Video Game Movies | url = https://entertainment.time.com/2008/10/20/top-10-worst-video-game-movies/slide/resident-evil-apocalypse-2004/ | work = [[時代雜誌|Time]] | date = 2008-10-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200626101600/https://entertainment.time.com/2008/10/20/top-10-worst-video-game-movies/slide/resident-evil-apocalypse-2004/ | archivedate = 2020-06-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2016年，[[恶心血腥|恶心血腥]]（{{lang|en|Bloody Disgusting}}）网站部分记者将本片评为《生化危机》系列最佳，但该网站另外一些记者又评为系列最差<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2018-06-20 | deadurl = no | date = 2016-04-13 | work = Bloody Disgusting | url = https://bloody-disgusting.com/editorials/3385605/apocalypse-worst-film-resident-evil/ | title = Unpopular Opinion: ‘Apocalypse’ is the Worst Film in the ‘Resident Evil’ Franchise | last = Thurman | first = Trace | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180620233748/http://bloody-disgusting.com/editorials/3385605/apocalypse-worst-film-resident-evil/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://bloody-disgusting.com/movie/3384859/rank-resident-evil-movies/ | title = How Would You Rank The ‘Resident Evil’ Movies? | last = Barkan | first = Jonathon | date = 2016-03-27 | work = Bloody Disgusting | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200301042526/https://bloody-disgusting.com/movie/3384859/rank-resident-evil-movies/ | archivedate = 2020-03-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2017年，{{lang|en|[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]}}网站的迈克尔·诺丁（{{lang|en|Michael Nordine}}）将本片评为《生化危机》系列最差，称电影唯一的可取之处不过是把前集扩展成系列电影，片中艾莉丝和复仇邪神的打斗场面实在愚蠢至极<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.thewrap.com/resident-evil-movies-ranked-final-chapter-milla-jovovich/ | title = All 6 ‘Resident Evil’ Movies, Ranked Worst to Best | last = Nordine | first = Michael | date = 2017-01-27 | work = [[TheWrap|TheWrap]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200603154253/https://www.thewrap.com/resident-evil-movies-ranked-final-chapter-milla-jovovich/ | archivedate = 2020-06-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

=== 获奖和提名 ===
