ocan.com/what-socan-does/socan-awards/?wpv_post_search=Jeff+Danna&wpv_aux_current_post_id=204&wpv_view_count=1964-TCPID204 | archivedate = 2020-08-21 | access-date = 2020-08-21}}</ref>。

